an></span><span style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#1A1814;\">실제 셀러 운영 시나리오 기반 <strong>케이스 스터디</strong></span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;\"><span style=\"width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;background:#F0E9DC;border:2px solid #B8860B;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;\"><span style=\"width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#B8860B;\"></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#1A1814;\">즉시 적용 가능한 <strong>SOP 워크플로</strong> 포함</span></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding-top:8px;\"><a href=\"#enroll\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:16px 36px;background:#3D2F1E;color:#FBF8F3;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;\">수강 신청하기</a><a href=\"#curriculum\" style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#3D2F1E;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid #3D2F1E;padding-bottom:2px;\">커리큘럼 보기 →</a></div></div><figure style=\"margin:0;position:relative;\"><img src=\"/assets/placeholder/hero-editorial.svg\" alt=\"CS 자동화 워크플로 일러스트\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;display:block;background:#F0E9DC;\"><figcaption style=\"margin-top:14px;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#3D2F1E;opacity:0.6;letter-spacing:0.05em;\">실제 수강생 CS 자동화 워크플로 예시</figcaption></figure></div>",
