        "html": "<div class=\"wrap\" style=\"position:relative;min-height:600px;background:#1E1510;overflow:hidden;display:flex;align-items:center;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:0;\"><img src=\"/assets/placeholder/hero-impact-bg.svg\" alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;opacity:0.18;\"></div><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(105deg,#1E1510 55%,transparent 100%);z-index:1;\"></div><div style=\"position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:88px 48px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:6fr 4fr;gap:48px;align-items:center;\"><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px;\"><div style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#2E2118;border:1px solid #D4A847;border-radius:100px;padding:6px 16px;width:fit-content;\"><span style=\"width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:#D4A847;\"></span><small style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#D4A847;\">Core Campus 신규 코스</small></div><h1 style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5.5vw,72px);font-weight:900;line-height:1.05;color:#F5EFE6;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin:0;\">CS 응대,<br><span style=\"color:#D4A847;\">Claude</span>가<br>대신합니다.</h1><p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(14px,1.6vw,17px);line-height:1.8;color:#F5EFE6;opacity:0.75;margin:0;max-width:480px;\">하루 1~3시간을 고객 문의에 쏟고 있다면,<br>지금 이 코스가 그 시간을 돌려드립니다.<br>프롬프트 하나로 완성되는 1인 사업가 CS 자동화.</p><div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;\"><a href=\"#enroll\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:18px 44px;background:#D4A847;color:#1E1510;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.02em;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;\">지금 시작하기</a><a href=\"#preview\" style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:18px 28px;border:1px solid rgba(245,239,230,0.35);color:#F5EFE6;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;\"><span style=\"width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid #F5EFE6;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><span style=\"width:0;height:0;border-style:solid;border-width:4px 0 4px 7px;border-color:transparent transparent transparent #F5EFE6;margin-left:1px;\"></span></span>미리보기</a></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:40px;padding-top:8px;border-top:1px solid rgba(245,239,230,0.12);\"><div><p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#D4A847;margin:0;line-height:1;\">28+</p><small style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#F5EFE6;opacity:0.55;\">프롬프트 템플릿</small></div><div><p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#D4A847;margin:0;line-height:1;\">4h</p><small style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#F5EFE6;opacity:0.55;\">총 강의 분량</small></div><div><p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#D4A847;margin:0;line-height:1;\">즉시</p><small style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#F5EFE6;opacity:0.55;\">적용 가능</small></div></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(46,33,24,0.85);border:1px solid rgba(212,168,71,0.25);border-radius:8px;padding:24px;backdrop-filter:blur(4px);\"><blockquote style=\"margin:0;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;color:#F5EFE6;opacity:0.85;\">&ldquo;환불 요청 답변을 Claude에게 맡겼더니<br>응답 시간이 4시간 → 12분으로 줄었어요.&rdquo;</blockquote><p style=\"margin:12px 0 0;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#D4A847;font-weight:600;\">— 핸드메이드 셀러, 수강생</p></div><div style=\"background:rgba(46,33,24,0.85);border:1px solid rgba(212,168,71,0.25);border-radius:8px;padding:24px;backdrop-filter:blur(4px);\"><blockquote style=\"margin:0;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;color:#F5EFE6;opacity:0.85;\">&ldquo;주말에도 CS가 쌓이는 게 제일 무서웠는데,<br>이제 월요일 아침이 두렵지 않습니다.&rdquo;</blockquote><p style=\"margin:12px 0 0;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#D4A847;font-weight:600;\">— 디지털 콘텐츠 판매자, 수강생</p></div></div></div></div>",
